==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Carthusian
<hw>Car*thu"sian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>Cartusianus</ets>, <ets>Cartusiensis</ets>, from the town of
<ets>Chartreuse</ets>, in France.]</ety> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld> <def>A
member of an exceeding austere religious order, founded at Chartreuse in
France by <person>St. Bruno</person>, in the year 1086.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Carthusian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Carthusian
<hw>Car*thu"sian</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to the
Carthusian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cartilage</ent>⟦br⟧
